overview: 20th Anniversary Rock collection (16 videos) featuring tunes from Aerosmith, the Cult, Red Hot Chili Peppers, Counting Crows and many others. Highlights include the mannequin-like models of Robert Palmer's "Addicted to Love," the zaniness of Blink-182's "All the Small Things" and the arresting visuals of Soundgarden's "Black Hole Sun."
title: MTV 20: Rock
